                             ;*  Error definitions file.
                             ;*  The macro to throw an error is elswhere, but 
                             ;*  It issues a 6502 BRK commmand with the next b
                             ;*  the error code.  The BRK handler then picks u
                             ;*  code and shows the appropriate message plus a
